# Documentation and private preparation records are not needed in images
docs/
**/docs/
*.md
**/*.md
!Reference/LightRAG/README.md
!Reference/Rag-anything/README.md
OPEN_SOURCE_CLEANUP_LOG.md
todolist.md
checklist.md

# Temporary files
.tmp_*/
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp
.cache/
.history/

# Operating-system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
